class=\"o\">:</span><span class=\"bp\">ğ•œ</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">simp</span> <span class=\"c1\">-- don't work</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>It's my problem. It seems that there are still some conditions about <code>\\bbk</code>. In fact, I don't understand this very well.</p>",
